com.tsgrp.migration.event.source.listener

Class QueueItemEventSourceListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.event.AbstractListener
      • com.tsgrp.migration.event.source.listener.QueueItemEventSourceListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SourceBeginExportNodeEventListener

    public class QueueItemEventSourceListener
extends AbstractListener
implements SourceBeginExportNodeEventListener
    Will take a queueItem and check to see if it has any associations that are versions. If it does, it will loop over the list of associated QueueItems. For each associated QueueItem, it will pad it's version label (000) and add the padded version label to a sorted Map. The padded version label will be the Sorted Map's key, the value will be the QueueItem's index in the List of associated QueueItems. Once all associated QueueItems have been processed, QueueItemEventSourceListener will reconstruct List of associated QueueItems and set the list as the associations for the QueueItem.
